title: Nuclear Bubble Wrap - Psycho Delicacy (320 kbps)
description:
"Psycho Delicacy" represents a new beginning for Nuclear Bubble Wrap. The award-winning band has recast itself as a psychedelic rock group in the vein of Ween and The Flaming Lips. Across the 21 madcap tracks that comprise the album the listener will experience an epic adventure into insanity featuring a variety of sounds and styles as presented only by the imaginations of Nuclear Bubble Wrap. Ambitious, funny, romantic, sad and frightening, "Psycho Delicacy" is the craziest trip of the year.
